.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-LIST" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-list \- list all wallets under WALLETS_ROOT
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-list
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scans
.B WALLETS_ROOT
(default
.IR ~/.lightning/wallets )
and returns each sub-directory as a wallet entry with a
.B has_db
flag indicating whether a
.I state.db
file is present.
Returns an empty array if the root directory does not exist.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{name, has_db}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-stats (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-check (1)
